{"tid":2431934,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"立場新聞建議香港人用食飯聲援緬甸被屠殺市民","createTime":"2021-03-04T03:47:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T11:01:53.000Z","uid":57328,"like":1,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"fb56d60feb72c7f6689fdc666a1af522a490b9dc","tid":2431934,"uid":57328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T03:47:46.000Z","msg":"// 最近緬甸局勢成為國際焦點，香港人除了網上聲援外，又可以做些甚麼？不如從吃入手吧！<br />\n<br />\n看似這麼遠那麼近的緬甸，名字在緬族人中其實有「遙遠的郊外」之意，換言之當地有豐富的自然資源，再加上緬甸民風純樸，就手取得的食材都可以入饌，再加上東南亞嗜辣的風俗，緬甸菜有很濃厚的鄉村風味，菜式鮮香鹹辣樣樣俱齊。<br />\n<br />\n不過原來香港的緬甸餐廳真幾近是零，在去年 7 月，香港才有一間由緬甸人 Nelson Htoo 開的 Club Rangoon。店面行歐式酒吧風的 Club Rangoon 名字來自緬甸最大城市仰光 (Yangon) 的另一寫法，或者就是想呈現緬甸另一迷人的面貌吧！ //<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3949234961828761/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F3949234961828761%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiX9TLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=97963a8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3949234961828761/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"f63d4686fd43823d5d8b8847c5edd18277c2a31e","tid":2431934,"uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T03:48:27.000Z","msg":"養肥軍政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83db732d8628543ee96cbcad44a8481650b8863d","tid":2431934,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T10:07:17.000Z","msg":"巴伊餐廳開左好耐啦 咩接近0"},{"pid":"cc98c5cb7fb1913bb50329379cef60f3d9202d11","tid":2431934,"uid":256041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83db732d8628543ee96cbcad44a8481650b8863d","tid":2431934,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T10:07:17.000Z","msg":"巴伊餐廳開左好耐啦 咩接近0"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T10:22:40.000Z","msg":"巴依係新疆野啊下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eb3199b6b7ab2162472c69ec6091c8be166eeef","tid":243193